subject: Dog Sledding
Women and Girls
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
lead_paragraph: Gender matters little in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race, in which mushers drive their dogs through extreme Alaskan terrain. Nearly a third of this year’s entrants were women.
